The paper deals with text spotting in natural scene images, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves deep learning techniques and multi-task training, which are common in sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
